public interface GTNetConfigEntityJpaRepositoryCustom extends BaseRepositoryCustom<GTNetConfigEntity>
Custom repository interface for GTNetConfigEntity operations. Provides attribute-level update functionality for editing entity-specific exchange configuration, logging preferences, and consumer usage priority.
